## Integration Examples

### Python SDK

```python
from augur import AUGURClient

client = AUGURClient(api_key="your_api_key")

# Register agent
agent = client.agents.register(
    name="customer-support-claude",
    type="claude-3-opus"
)

# Generate fingerprint
fingerprint = client.fingerprint.generate(agent.id)
print(f"Fingerprint confidence: {fingerprint.confidence}%")

# Verify identity
result = client.fingerprint.verify(
    agent_id=agent.id,
    recent_actions=get_recent_actions()
)

if not result.verified:
    send_alert(f"Agent verification failed: {result.similarity_score}%")
```

### JavaScript/TypeScript

```typescript
import { AUGURClient } from '@augur/sdk';

const client = new AUGURClient({ apiKey: 'your_api_key' });

// Monitor for drift
async function monitorDrift(agentId: string) {
